{"tid":1270243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑色，代表香港人永不投降","createTime":"2019-06-30T20:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T20:53:56.000Z","uid":12404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0536d3a57b1933a35542beee091f8c50fba48df","tid":1270243,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ1aMX4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ1aMX4.png&h=b7bb82a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑旗，白旗之相反，代表永不言敗<br />\n<br />\n洋紫荊，代表香港，本身不能結果，但靠人的努力得以延續<br />\n<br />\n紅色，代表香港烈士嘅血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://img.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F01%2F033458_2eb12d2f4fa610dc032bd51026819922.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%252Fupload%252F2019%252F07%252F01%252F033458_2eb12d2f4fa610dc032bd51026819922.png&h=f9db037d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d887fc0a02dfc37138562d2187681a1d5562f","tid":1270243,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T20:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}